ime":"2018-03-12T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"一般黎講降落係危險過起飛，主要係因為速度，takeoff 一過左v1(取消界限) 直到v2(安全界限，過左先可以抽多啲頭) 都係危險期但係其實只要個pilot 唔抽過龍，就冇問題，有咩事推平部機都易解決，因為本身thruster最高唔洗點反應。<br />\n相反landing ，過左approaching minimum 之後其實就好慢，同一個air speed 唔開flap 一早stall左，而且因為AS 低，風既影響會大過takeoff 好多，仲有thrust 都係低左好多，有起事上黎部機都唔可以極快加速(反應同engine 問題)。"},{"pid":"86f68c7b3472257d8847bd0273cfcd0cd25c295f","tid":589464,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a42e14ca9f4cb9dfcaaa4d2b87e662dd10f899f","tid":589464,"uid":172650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛機失事仲難過撞車<br />\n咪on9<br />\n你平時搭車係咪驚到賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撞車易啲生環，飛機失事就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"你都識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就無事，一有事你有救生衣都無撚用<br />\n<br />\n但你記住，可能遇上99999次車禍都好難有一次飛機失事，更何況你唔係成日搭"},{"pid":"9a34988e9965557ce97d29132007060a1f7d6548","tid":589464,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬係垃圾00後定蝗蟲新移民？<br />\n大鄉里未坐過飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚就騎牛算啦"},{"pid":"c7f5e33bc7f2ee9b2995db9ed0d5b8d861492e38","tid":589464,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好搭廉航，擇大機，有咁貴搭咁貴，出事意外率減半"},{"pid":"cb3c16e31772f4603a198954d0ca2754f2bec1ff","tid":589464,"uid":4166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"引擎唔識轉果陣時<br />\n利引：業界人仕"},{"pid":"1bbfebb3f07da730c3f9b4ef1a94de953fe93aa5","tid":589464,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109c21b4e5f943b0cef175894a4d2241a71aa0b1","tid":589464,"uid":172650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>起飛個時?未穩定搖搖欲墜，好似就跌就跌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係飛到好高有氣流個陣?氣流太勁會唔會搞到墜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或係準備降落個時機頭向下瘋狂轉彎，好似向下衝咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定會係見到機場要降落，飛到好低個時?搖到就黎墜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答到我，每次搭飛機都驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>知道你都改變唔到d咩  <br />\n一係唔好去 一係搭船 搭鳩鐵</blockquote><br />\n知道我起碼可以打醒12分精神，有咩事即刻著救生衣走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>落得海你都死撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通過起飛同降落最易出事，機翼有積雪，電路問題令到機械故障/產生火燭，機長on99整錯setting 呢d常見小小。<br />\n因為事出突然，多數都Rip <br />\n<br />\n中間開哂auto，唔會點出事。<br />\n就算賴左野，都有幾萬尺高度比佢解決/搵位降落。</blockquote><br />\n我見啲空難幾乎冇生環者，係咪有起事上黎實死冇生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"睇咩事先得，<br />\n火燭可以即刻祈禱<br />\n水上降落，冇事係萬中無一<br />\n冇左個引擎s, 都大機會冇事"},{"pid":"80d35cb669659c530cbfe37ee64a14c9ec50a688","tid":589464,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"死咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起馬你屋企人都有錢先"},{"pid":"6c3d996f654f199d11cdcf692160f30d0dfedde1","tid":589464,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30571a61507347e06defe2861b4b89fc9ab2d749","tid":589464,"uid":172650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>起飛個時?未穩定搖搖欲墜，好似就跌就跌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係飛到好高有氣流個陣?氣流太勁會唔會搞到墜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或係準備降落個時機頭向下瘋狂轉彎，好似向下衝咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=